{"word":"G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis - Assurance","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πίστις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pístis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pis'-tis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Assurance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"விசுவாசம், நிச்சயம், உண்மை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"faith"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a>; <i>persuasion</i>, that is, <i>credence</i>; moral <i>conviction</i> (of <i>religious</i> truth, or the truthfulness of God or a religious teacher), especially <i>reliance</i> upon Christ for salvation; abstractly <i>constancy</i> in such profession; by extension the system of religious (Gospel) <i>truth</i> itself: - assurance, belief, believe, faith, fidelity."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3640 - ὀλιγόπιστος - oligópistos - ol-ig-op'-is-tos/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos'/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104 - πιστόω - pistóō - pis-to'-o/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569 - ἀπιστέω - apistéō - ap-is-teh'-o/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570 - ἀπιστία - apistía - ap-is-tee'-ah/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'-is-tos/571\">G571</a>"}]}